Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:07.71,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无情地发出宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:20.57,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你用双耳 独自聆听着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:33.42,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我的眼睛 映照出久远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.77,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选择什么 放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.98,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我如何能 自行定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:43.19,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}选取之物 早已在心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.21,0:01:46.12,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}向神问询 是否有误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:49.24,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实不曾孤独过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:51.79,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}其实一直在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:58.86,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}现在 伸出手去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:02.10,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}已经无所畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:05.61,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}哪怕化身怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:13.69,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我一定 会做到
