Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我就是个没什么劲头的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 今天中午就出出血
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用限量美食牛舌咖喱 来给你鼓劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限量美食…买得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的能力面前 小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久候多时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你应该先去趟医院
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说是家常便饭 让你操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力的缺陷实在太大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又香又辣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是咖喱！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合你胃口就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱果然要吃辣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是中等辣度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就喜欢这种辣味是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛舌也很嫩 棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你很爱吃咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 啊…我终于想起了这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助者又要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去学生会室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么他总是浑身湿透？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿好衣服全身湿透才能用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻烦的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.84,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是 通灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降灵术 让死者的灵魂附在自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮来那种
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.23,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)\an8\fs56\fscx92\fsp1}潮来：日本的一种巫女，能召唤死者附身于己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不是装神弄鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是可用的特殊能力么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然身怀两种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很想立即去抓人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里 只是条寻常路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方在赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在工作日的午间赶路？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翘课了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条路 应该是无人问津的小巷来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们先去现场看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？就是这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来 那个人经过这里时很匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这一面没灰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来对方是在奔跑中撞到了箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个对象 在被人追赶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先往前走走看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两种新留下的脚印…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种步子小 一种步子大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就是有女孩在被大人追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你说刚才那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像被大汉追着跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在拍戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫西森柚咲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字好熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是步未喜欢的那个偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也在「哈罗哈罗」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是How-low-hello乐队担任主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能唱能跳的当红偶像 说的就是她！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原来是个偶像宅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学六年级时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她参加青少年时尚杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「小香蕉」举办的第14届读者模特海选
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一举夺魁 并出道成为杂志专属模特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年后 她成为「早间气氛」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节目的固定班底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又过了两年 她为复习迎考退出节目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上高中后 她又重回演艺界…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 回到话题上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是用特殊能力惹了祸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才被人追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:07:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事地球人都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隶属Clex事务所…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打电话问问事务所吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是艺人啊 事务所会理你才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙坂同学 靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挨疼的人可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种战术能不用就别用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是为此而请你加盟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 搞坏摄像机你赔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为这个生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒要问你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来就给你叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再耗下去 你会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是受托办事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.75,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍了这条命也不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我在找西森柚咲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁委托的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳电视台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视台的谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经给你叫了救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在找名叫西森柚咲的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.32,0:08:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称「柚咲琳」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找来干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么 她正被人追赶着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们和柚咲很熟？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忠实粉丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老打断我的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在旁边看着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底是怎么打倒那个男人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了特殊的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,类似于…西森身上的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能帮她的忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 那就证明给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证明你有她那样的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力并不相同啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否信服了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你们一定会困惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事挺复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己确认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇噻 俱乐部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用把这种角落都录下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边 别磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！是货真价实的柚咲琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗的CD我全有！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.69,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是电视上那位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这些是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美砂一样 这些人也有特殊能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的真名不是柚咲 而是美砂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很难解释…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人真的可信么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们使用力量 将外面的人打跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我直接问她几个问题行不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是问些莫名其妙的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你吃不了兜着走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 这么凶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友利 谨慎小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫友利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是西森柚咲 柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己叫自己「柚咲琳」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次和偶像面对面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真可爱 像个洋娃娃一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和你面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 先告诉我你的真名好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑羽柚咲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真名反而更像艺名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 经常有人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是「黑羽」实在是没有偶像的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就换成了「西森」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么黑羽同学 你知道你有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成另一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确没自觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘没问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 黑羽同学请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 我像是得了嗜睡病一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就会睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来时到了别的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是最近的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生说我「可能有多重人格」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 你不是多重人格
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------TXTB----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和我们一样 是特殊能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让死者的灵魂附在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是用这个能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫出了你们说的「美砂」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都别问
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是比柚咲大一岁的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半年前 死于事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对陌生人说这么多 想死啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是美砂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁大点地方挤这么多人 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格陡变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好厉害的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点 美砂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想烧死大家么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太没味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附身的主动权 原来在美砂手上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有意见么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是个有些缺陷的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 柚咲是稀有的附身体质
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而附上身来的美砂则有着燃烧的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.13,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两位是你什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我活着时和他们一起疯过 我们是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道令妹为什么被人追赶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲从某个片场错拿了这个回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电视台大制作人的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲不小心读了里面的短信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挪用公款 勾结坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交给警察 他肯定会受处分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关机了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是昨天没关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么通过GPS 这个藏身地已经暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 还了手机也不可能太平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果交给警察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.44,0:14:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出卖制作人的黑羽 就没法在演艺圈混了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就把电视台整个烧了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货！你妹妹会被逮捕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭丫头 你算哪根葱？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让妹妹进少年劳教所么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太没味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想救你妹妹对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就齐心协力 反过来吓吓他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胜算？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最擅长制定吓唬人的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信我没错的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很爽气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我听你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.01,0:15:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听美砂的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我刚才是不是又睡着了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是累坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.61,0:15:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 吃点烤棉花糖 定定神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 棉花糖变成了新鲜烤棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 我到底该如何面对柚咲琳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无头绪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吓人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我们先去特种服装店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位需要防火服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.08,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝不下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.96,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都没怎么喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于肯出来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己逃不掉了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…我完全弄不懂你们追赶我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我柚咲琳做坏事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的手机还来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.10,0:16:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还回去后 柚咲琳会不会有危险呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这演艺圈 反正已经没未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账 你才没未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再烧一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你把我逼上了绝路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实正好相反啊 还不明白么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太没味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是西森柚咲么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是柚咲琳 西森柚咲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为了成功 想杀就杀 比如他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦 全都清理掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.93,0:17:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等…你…你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你个头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发 发生了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 随时都能把你葬进黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 我投降 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住 不许再犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就二话不说 灭了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 是你们帮了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还以为一切都是柚咲干的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作人以后肯定不敢违抗柚咲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 话可不能说死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.16,0:18:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你转入我们星海学园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.35,0:18:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后和我们一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才已经说明过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.02,0:18:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦被科学家抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会天天接受人体实验
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也无法正常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校和配套的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对黑羽来说 是全日本最安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确对柚咲有帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！那…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚咲的力量消失后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就再也见不到美砂了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也想问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是这样没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但美砂已经去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死后还能再见 本就是违反自然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶 她说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此作别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 在最后 让我表白心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 却说不出话来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？晶 原来你对我有意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂 我一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人害臊 是恋爱的喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你 在我表白前就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑助力车带人 出事后我只受了点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却…被我害死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你背了个大包袱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 追求刺激的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 太不像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶 忘了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天起 过你自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别老想着一个死人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然你的人生一团糟 就没法幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 真让人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美砂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续走我的路 哪怕没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会舍弃对你的眷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.52,0:20:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个 都要活得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 真是多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.24,0:20:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我过得 快乐极了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漫长的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚死啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚回家 要打电话告知的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也…你这么晚还没睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭要一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是乙坂家家传祖训的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.04,0:21:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是在忙学生会的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬出这种理由 我无法反驳的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 今晚你做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.55,0:21:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得意之作 意大利肉酱面的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又是哈罗哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.61,0:21:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是同一个人物啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？谁和谁相同？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 西森柚咲和她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.52,0:22:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她本人？她是你的熟人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.19,0:22:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这事也没禁止我说出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…告诉她也不要紧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 她会转到我们学校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶？真令人羡慕的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.92,0:22:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否有机会见到她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 机会总是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.79,0:22:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 先擦鼻血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真了不得的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:30.65,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}了不得的说 真了不得的说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 兴奋过头了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//----------------------------EDCN----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:43.21,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}如果我说 旅途的艰险等在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:49.10,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你一定 会如此斥责我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:55.75,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你会说 活着就是残酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:23:02.26,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你会说 谁都有切肤之痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.64,0:23:06.93,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}总有一天 我要向你展示
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:14.30,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}展示一件 珍藏心中之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.59,0:23:22.93,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}独一无二的奔流 涌现后便即消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:29.27,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}经历着失去的你 默默遥望云端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:35.58,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你一定 还在坚信乐园定能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:58.34,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be2\fad(150,150)}你一定 是为藏在深处的我欢笑至今




